f>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=9 March 2020|accessdate=7 March 2020}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Belgium|award=Gold|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2020|accessdate=13 March 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Canada|artist=Lewis Capaldi|title=Before You Go|award=Platinum|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2020|accessdate=19 March 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Italy|artist=Lewis Capaldi|title=Before You Go|award=Gold|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2020|salesamount=35,000|accessdate=24 February 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=New Zealand|artist=Lewis Capaldi|title=Before You Go|award=Platinum|type=single|relyear=2019|relmonth=11|recent=website|id=4828|accessdate=7 March 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|artist=Lewis Capaldi|title=Before You Go|award=Platinum|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2020|id=16089-4876-1|accessdate=14 February 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|streaming=true}}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n! Country\n! Date\n! Format\n! Label\n! {{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Various\n| 19 November 2019\n| {{hlist|[[Music download|Digital download]]|[[Streaming media|streaming]]}}\n| rowspan=\"3\"| {{hlist|[[Vertigo Records|Vertigo Berlin]]|[[Universal Music Group|Universal]]}}\n| <ref name=\"NME\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"| United Kingdom\n| 22 November 2019\n| [[Contemporary hit radio]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191122202513/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/articles/3tqPdBWF9yMbTrfjWvfKV8t/radio-1-playlist|title=Radio 1 Playlist|website=[[BBC]]|accessdate=7 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 7 December 2019\n| [[Adult contemporary radio]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/articles/2qNJsnjYFvbLrK9CZ0CfYfM/radio-2-new-music-playlist|title=Radio 2 New Music Playlist|website=[[BBC]]|accessdate=7 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Italy\n| 13 December 2019\n| Contemporary hit radio\n| Universal\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://radiodate.it/radio-date/lewis-capaldi-before-you-go-190089-13-12-2019-radiodate/|title=Before You Go LEWIS CAPALDI|website=Radio Date|accessdate=7 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"| United States\n| 6 January 2020\n| Adult contemporary radio\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Capitol Records|Capitol]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allaccess.com/hot-modern-ac/future-releases|title=Hot/Modern/AC Future Releases|website=All Access|accessdate=4 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 7 January 2020\n| Contemporary hit radio\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allaccess.com/top40-mainstream/future-releases|title=Top 40/M Future Releases|website=All Access|accessdate=4 December 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Lewis Capaldi}}\n\n[[Category:2019 singles]]\n[[Category:2019 songs]]\n[[Category:Irish Singles Chart number-one singles]]\n[[Category:Lewis Capaldi songs]]\n[[Category:Songs about suicide]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Lewis Capaldi]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Ben Kohn]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Peter Kelleher (songwriter)]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Tom Barnes (songwriter)]]\n[[Category:Song recordings produced by TMS (production team)]]\n[[Category:UK Singles Chart number-one singles]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = Before You Go\n| cover      =\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Lewis Capaldi]]\n| album      = [[Divinely Uninspired to a Hellish Extent]] {{noitalic|(extended edition)}}\n| released   = {{start date|2019|11|19|df=y}}\n| format     =\n* [[Music download|Digital download]]\n* [[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| recorded   =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = <!-- Please source genres -->\n| length     = {{duration|m=3|s=36}}\n| label      =\n* [[Vertigo Records|Vertigo Berlin]]\n* [[Universal Music Group|Universal]]\n| writer     =\n* Lewis Capaldi\n* [[TMS (production team)|Ben Kohn]]\n* [[TMS (production team)|Pete Kelleher]]\n* Phil Plested\n* [[TMS (production team)|Tom Bames]]\n| producer   = [[TMS (production team)|TMS]]\n| prev_title = [[Hold Me While You Wait]]\n| prev_year  = 2019\n| next_title =\n| next_year  =\n| misc       =\n}}\n\"'''Before You Go'''\" is a song by Scottish singer-songwriter [[Lewis Capaldi]], released as a single from the extended edition of his debut studio album ''[[Divinely Uninspired to a Hellish Extent]]'' on 19 November 2019. The song was made available upon pre-order of the extended edition.<ref name=\"NME\">{{cite web|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/lewis-capaldi-reflects-absolutely-wild-2019-before-you-go-2569609|title=Lewis Capaldi reflects on \"absolutely wild\" 2019 on new track \"Before You Go\" \u2013 listen|last=Skinner|first=Tom|website=[[NME]]|date=19 November 2019|accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref> The song was sent to US radio stations on January 6, 2020 as his second US single. It reached number one on the [[Irish Singles Chart]] in November 2019 and on the [[UK Singles Chart]] in January 2020, becoming Capaldi's second chart-topper in the UK and third in Ireland.\n\n==Background and composition==\nAbout the song, Capaldi revealed in a social media post that it \"is by far the most personal tune\" he has ever written and stated that the previous year has been \"absolutely wild\" for him.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.spinsouthwest.com/music/lewis-capaldi-releases-new-track-go-926862|title=Lewis Capaldi Releases New Track \"Before You Go\"|last=Lucey|first=Tuathla|website=[[Spin South West]]|date=19 November 2019|accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref> According to ''[[Idolator (website)|Idolator]]'', the song \"deals with the emotional aftermath of suicide\", and was inspired by the suicide of Capaldi\u2019s aunt while Capaldi was a child.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.idolator.com/7903230/lewis-capaldi-new-single-before-you-go|title=Lewis Capaldi Releases Poignant New Single \"Before You Go\"|last=Wass|first=Mike|website=[[Idolator (website)|Idolator]]|date=19 November 2019|accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Critical reception==\nGary James of ''Entertainment Focus'' described the song as an \"emotional track\".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.entertainment-focus.com/uncategorized/lewis-capaldi-releases-most-personal-song-yet-with-before-you-go/|title=Lewis Capaldi releases most personal song yet with Before You Go|last=James|first=Gary|website=Entertainment Focus|date=19 November 2019|accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref> Maxamillion Polo of ''Ones to Watch'' thought that the song \"is a tried-and-true song of heartbreak, one that is not looking to place blame but solve those questions lacking answers\" and questioned if Capaldi's emotional tone was \"the result of a greater sense of loss\".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.onestowatch.com/blog/lewis-capaldi-reflects-in-before-you-go-his|title=Lewis Capaldi Reflects in \"Before You Go,\" His Most Personal Tune to Date|last=Polo|first=Maxamillion|website=Ones to Watch|date=19 November 2019|accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref> ''[[Clash (magazine)#ClashMusic.com|Clash Music]]'''s Robin Murray called the track \"trademark Capaldi\", further describing it as \"a rousing piece of acoustic songwriting with a driving vocal\".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.clashmusic.com/news/lewis-capaldi-shares-new-single-before-you-go|title=Lewis Capaldi Shares New Single \"Before You Go\"|last=Murray|first=Robin|website=[[Clash (magazine)#ClashMusic.com|Clash Music]]|date=19 November 2019|accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Stream<ref>{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/0488X5veBK6t3vSmIiTDJY|title=Before You Go|website=[[Spotify]]|accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref>\n| title1 = Before You Go\n| length1 = 3:36\n| title2 = [[Bruises (Lewis Capaldi song)|Bruises]]\n| length2 = 3:38\n}}\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits adapted from [[Tidal (service)|Tidal]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://listen.tidal.com/album/122351387/track/122351390|title=Before You Go / Lewis Capaldi \u2013 Tidal|website=[[Tidal (service)|Tidal]]|accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Lewis Capaldi]] \u2013 songwriting, vocals\n* [[TMS (production team)|Ben Kohn]] \u2013 songwriting, production, bass guitar\n* [[TMS (production team)|Pete Kelleher]] \u2013 songwriting, production, keyboards\n* [[TMS (production team)|Tom Bames]] \u2013 songwriting, production, drums\n* Phil Plested \u2013 songwriting, background vocals\n* Vern Asbury \u2013 guitar\n* Rory Dewar - Art Design\n* Lewis Capaldi - A&R\n* Ryan Walter - A&R\n* Robert Vosgien \u2013 master engineering\n* [[Spike Stent|Mark \"Spike\" Stent]] \u2013 mixing\n* Chris Bishop \u2013 vocal engineering\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019\u20132020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{single chart|Australia|7|artist=Lewis Capaldi|song=Before You Go|rowheader=true|accessdate=29 February 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Austria|20|artist=Lewis Capaldi|song=Before You Go|rowheader=true|accessdate=19 March 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders|2|artist=Lewis Capaldi|song=Before You Go|rowheader=true|accessdate=21 March 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Wallonia|4|artist=Lewis Capaldi|song=Before You Go|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Canada|27|artist=Lewis Capaldi|rowheader=true|accessdate=10 March 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Czech Republic|1|year=2020|week=11|rowheader=true|accessdate=17 March 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Czechdigital|21|year=2020|week=12|rowheader=true|accessdate=24 March 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Denmark ([[Tracklisten]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hitlisten.nu/default.asp?w=11&y=2020&list=t40|title=Track Top-40 Uge 11, 2020|publisher=[[Hitlisten]]|accessdate=25 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 18\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Ecuador ([[National-Report]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.national-report.com/top-ecuador/|title=Top 100 Ecuador|publisher=[[National-Report]]|accessdate=3 April 2020|language=Spanish|archiveurl=http://archive.today/PCqyn|archivedate=3 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 64\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| France ([[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|SNEP]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://snepmusique.com/les-tops/le-top-de-la-semaine/top-albums/?semaine=15?&annee=2020&categorie=Top%20Singles|title=Top Singles (Week 15, 2020)|publisher=[[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique]]|language=French|accessdate=14 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 49\n|-\n{{single chart|Germany2|42|songid=1921258|artist=Lewis Capaldi|song=Before You Go|rowheader=true|accessdate=21 February 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Hungary|21|year=2020|week=14|rowheader=true|accessdate=10 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Hungarysingle|26|year=2020|week=8|rowheader=true|accessdate=28 February 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Hungarystream|39|year=2020|week=7|rowheader=true|accessdate=22 February 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Ireland ([[Irish Recorded Music Association|IRMA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://irma.ie/index.cfm?page=irish-charts&chart=Singles|title=IRMA \u2013 Irish Charts|publisher=[[Irish Recorded Music Association]]|accessdate=30 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Italy ([[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|FIMI]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fimi.it/top-of-the-music/classifiche.kl#/charts/3/2020/8|title=Top Singoli \u2013 Classifica settimanale WK 8|publisher=[[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana]]|language=Italian|accessdate=22 February 2020}}</ref>\n| 17\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Lithuania ([[AGATA (organization)|AGATA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.agata.lt/lt/naujienos/savaites-klausomiausi-w48/|title=2019 48-os savait\u0117s klausomiausi (TOP 100)|language=Lithuanian|publisher=[[AGATA (organization)|AGATA]]|date=29 November 2019|accessdate=29 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 29\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Malaysia ([[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|RIM]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/RecordingIndustryMalaysia/photos/pcb.3315800078447339/3315799791780701/?type=3&theater|title=Top 20 Most Streamed International & Domestic Singles In Malaysia|work=[[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia]]|publisher=Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|accessdate=22 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 6\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch40|2|year=2020|week=11|rowheader=true|accessdate=14 March 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch100|7|artist=Lewis Capaldi|song=Before You Go|rowheader=true|accessdate=7 March 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand ([[Recorded Music NZ]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4820|title=NZ Top 40 Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=17 February 2020|accessdate=15 February 2020}}</ref>\n| 9\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Norway ([[VG-lista]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vglista.no/topplister/topp-20-single-2019-48/|title=VG-lista \u2013 Topp 20 Single uke 48, 2019|publisher=[[VG-lista]]|accessdate=30 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 9\n|-\n{{single chart|Poland|7|chartid=3362|year=2020|rowheader=true|accessdate=6 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Portugal|70|artist=Lewis Capaldi|song=Before You Go|rowheader=true|accessdate=12 March 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Scotland|1|date=20191122|rowheader=true|accessdate=23 November 2019}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Singapore ([[Recording Industry Association (Singapore)|RIAS]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rias.org.sg/rias-top-charts/|title=RIAS International Top Charts Week 13|publisher=Recording Industry Association (Singapore)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403095609/https://www.rias.org.sg/rias-top-charts/|archive-date=3 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 13\n|-\n{{single chart|Slovakia|5|year=2020|week=14|rowheader=true|accessdate=7 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Slovakdigital|34|year=2020|week=12|rowheader=true|accessdate=24 March 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Slovenia ([[SloTo